title: Pat Martino shares his inspirational Story at Música Creativa in Madrid

http_headers.User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/70.0.3532.3 Safari/537.36

description: One of the greatest guitarists in jazz, Pat Martino suffered a severe brain aneurysm and underwent surgery after being told that his condition could be terminal. After his operations he could remember almost nothing. He barely recognized his parents. And had no memory of his guitar or his career. In his Master Class at Escuela de Música Creativa in Madrid, he shared his inspirational story. This is how Pat made a remarkable recovery and 17 years later managed to play the guitar again http://www.musicacreativa.com/
fulltitle: Pat Martino shares his inspirational Story at Música Creativa in Madrid
